OL,3,CIranian man and Romanian woman charged
OL,4,Cover incident at Scottish submarine
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,FAn Iranian man and a Romanian woman
OL,8,Fhave been charged after two people
OL,9,Ftried to enter the naval base which is
OL,10,Fthe home of the UK's nuclear deterrent.
OL,12,FA 34-year-old man and a 31-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman were charged following the
OL,14,Fincident at HM Naval Base Clyde, which
OL,15,Fis known as Faslane.
OL,17,FA statement from Police Scotland said:
OL,18,F"Around 5pm on Thursday, March 19,
OL,19,F2026 we were made aware of two people
OL,20,Fattempting to enter HM Naval Base
OL,21,FClyde.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
