OL,3,CIranian man and Romanian woman charged
OL,4,Cover incident at Scottish submarine
OL,5,Cbase
OL,7,F"A 34-year-old Iranian man and a 31-
OL,8,Fyear-old Romanian woman have been
OL,9,Farrested and charged in connection
OL,10,Fwith the incident.
OL,12,F"They are due to appear at Dumbarton
OL,13,FSheriff Court on Monday, March 23.
OL,14,FInquiries are ongoing."
OL,16,FFaslane is home to the core of the
OL,17,FUK's submarine fleet and the Trident
OL,18,Fnuclear deterrent.
